videos.description: Michigan State's Gavin Schilling receives the pass in transition and attacks the rim.
videos.headline: Schilling smashes a monstrous fast-break dunk

videos.description: Eli Cain nails a buzzer-beating 3-pointer to tie DePaul with Michigan State at halftime.
videos.headline: Cain beats the halftime buzzer

videos.description: Tre'Darius McCallum finds open space in the paint for a wide-open dunk.
videos.headline: McCallum slips free for dunk

videos.description: Matt McQuaid's fifth 3-pointer of the night helps increase the Spartans' lead over DePaul.
videos.headline: McQuaid drains his 5th three of the night

videos.description: Matt McQuaid sets a new career high in points after hitting his sixth 3-pointer.
videos.headline: McQuaid's 6th three of the night sets a career high

videos.description: Michigan State uses all the fundamentals on offense to create an easy basket.
videos.headline: Spartans use six passes to set up layup

videos.description: Michigan State breaks DePaul's full court press with a powerful alley-oop finish to go up by 20.
videos.headline: Spartans break the press with authority

videos.description: Michigan State head coach Tom Izzo says he is happy with how the defense and offense came out and played in the second half during the victory over DePaul.
videos.headline: Izzo breaks down the Spartans' win over DePaul
